#1 Reaction:   One night, many years ago, pre-game, Lakers warming up, Jack is already sitting in his courtside seat.  The stands are starting to fill in....   A drop dead gorgeous, 20ish Asian woman, wearing a pink dress, with the hem line at mid-thigh, wearing a pushup bra and putting on quite a show, walks down the stairs, out of the shadows into the light...   When she starts to side shuffle to reach her seat directly behind Jack, the entire place sees her and starts applauding, whistling, cheering, etc..... Just when every guy's tongue was scraping the floor.....  Jack stands up and jokingly takes a bow, as if the cheering was for him.   The whole place erupted in laughter !!   The young woman blushed and quietly sat down !
